---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Our Services">
  <h1>Our Services</h1>
  <p>At Moises Auto Body & Paint, we offer a wide range of services to meet your automotive needs. Below are some of the services we provide:</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Paint and Cosmetic Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/auto-painting`}>Auto Painting</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/car-detailing`}>Car Detailing</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/custom-paint`}>Custom Paint</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/dent-removal`}>Dent Removal</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/paintless-dent-removal`}>Paintless Dent Removal</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/paint-and-cosmetic/rust-removal`}>Rust Removal</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Collision and Frame Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/collision-and-frame/bumper-repair`}>Bumper Repair</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/collision-and-frame/collision-repair`}>Collision Repair</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/collision-and-frame/frame-alignment`}>Frame Alignment</a></li>
      <li><a href={`${base}services/collision-and-frame/frame-straightening`}>Frame Straightening</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <p>For more information about each service, please click on the links above.</p>
</Layout>